                      <li>Pre-course experience: None</li>
                      <li>Duration: 2 days, usually over a weekend with a combination of both-shore based theory session and practical</li>
                      <li>Minimum age: 12 (candidates under the age of 16 will be issued with an endorsed certificate)</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="card">
