                    <p>If you need a flight to Malta International, the airport code is MLA. There is only one airport in Malta.</p>
                    <p>On arrival at Malta airport, there is a kiosk at the exit from the airport where you can pre pay the taxi to the boat. The cost of this is usually 25 Euro.The taxi drivers speak good English.</p>
                    <p>Cheaper transport option would be use taxi app such as: Bolt, Ecab, Cool. There are plenty of taxi connected to these apps.</p>
                    <p>You will have a short safety brief on arrival to familiarise yourself with the boat and meet your crew mates!</p>
